PRIVATE EVENTS

We would love to host you for your next event!

Our space features an indoor bar as well as indoor and outdoor seating and standing room. The capacity of our space is 40 people. We are able to serve all of our famous, hand-crafted cocktails as well as beer, wine and food at events.

For more information about hosting an event at Dalila’s, download our Private Events Information Package below or contact us directly at .
